### =========================
### MOVIES - CRUD + LIST
### =========================

### ✅ LIST
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies?page=1&size=10

### ❌ LIST ERROR
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies?page=abc&size=xyz


### ✅ CREATE
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": -1,
  "title": "Inception",
  "year": 2010,
  "description": "A skilled thief who enters dreams."
}

### ❌ CREATE ERROR
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  title: Inception
}


### ✅ READ ONE
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies/1

### ❌ READ ONE ERROR
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies/9999


### ✅ UPDATE
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Joker 2",
  "year": 2020,
  "description": "A man that is a joke."
}

### ❌ UPDATE ERROR
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies/1


### ✅ DELETE
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies/1

### ❌ DELETE ERROR
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/movies/abc